If you want the cleanest settings IA for the current backend, I would use:
1.
Profile
2.
Security
3.
Membership
4.
Routines
5.
Saved Gyms
6.
Access History
7.
Payments
Payments / Billing history is not ready as a real settings section. You have payment processing and a payment-attempt model in PaymentAttempt.java, plus gateway status DTOs in PaymentAttemptStatusResponse.java, but there is no /users/me/payments list/detail endpoint.
True user routine settings are only partial. The model has currentDay, cyclesCompleted, activatedAt, deactivatedAt, and lastSessionAt in UserRoutineSetting.java, but there is no dedicated /users/me/routine-settings endpoint.
